                                                                                                                                Messaging

                                                                                                                                Message card

                                                                                                                                A message card is a card component optimized for message campaign content.

                                                                                                                                Usage
                                                                                                                                Specs
                                                                                                                                Status & changelog

                                                                                                                                Metrics

                                                                                                                                Artwork tailing
                                                                                                                                Artwork top

                                                                                                                                Spacing

                                                                                                                                These are the default spacing metrics for the card, but the spacing between type and button elements can be customized in order to accommodate custom type sizes.

                                                                                                                                Artwork trailing

                                                                                                                                Headline + button tertiary
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                Note Tertiary buttons require different spacing so the text in the button lines up with the leading edge of the heading and paragraph.

                                                                                                                                Headline + button pill
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                Since tertiary Buttons already have white space, they require less surrounding space to look visually balanced. Tertiary Buttons have a top spacing of 4, while secondary Buttons have 12.

                                                                                                                                Headline + paragraph + Button tertiary
                                                                                                                                Headline + paragraph + button pill
                                                                                                                                Headline + paragraph

                                                                                                                                Artwork top

                                                                                                                                Headline + button tertiary
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                Note tertiary Buttons require different spacing so the text in the Button lines up with the leading edge of the heading and paragraph

                                                                                                                                Headline + button secondary
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                Since tertiary Buttons already have white space, they require less surrounding space to look visually balanced. Tertiary Buttons have a top spacing of 4, while secondary Buttons have 12.

                                                                                                                                Headline + paragraph
                                                                                                                                Headline + paragraph + button secondary
                                                                                                                                Headline + paragraph + button tertiary

                                                                                                                                Type and color

                                                                                                                                Typography

                                                                                                                                Typography in the card is set to default sizes but can be customized to bump up or down the text sizes.

                                                                                                                                Type

                                                                                                                                Color

                                                                                                                                See also, Color logic to understand what is considered a "light" or "dark" background color.

                                                                                                                                Light background color card
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                Card background: [any light primitive color]

                                                                                                                                Content: ContentOnColorInverse(Black)

                                                                                                                                Button background: backgroundAlwaysLight(White)

                                                                                                                                Button text: contentOnColorInverse(Black)

                                                                                                                                Border:1px border opaque

                                                                                                                                Dismiss button background: backgroundAlwaysLight(white) at 60% opacity

                                                                                                                                Dismiss icon color:ContentOnColorInverse(Black)

                                                                                                                                Dark background color card
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                Background: [Any dark primitive color]

                                                                                                                                Text: contentOnColor

                                                                                                                                Button background: backgroundAlwaysLight(white)

                                                                                                                                Button text: contentOnColorInverse(Black)

                                                                                                                                Border: none

                                                                                                                                Dismiss button background: backgroundAlwaysDark(black) at 40% opacity

                                                                                                                                Dismiss icon color:ContentOnColor(White)

                                                                                                                                White background color card
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                Card background: backgroundAlwaysLight(White)

                                                                                                                                Content: ContentOnColorInverse(Black)

                                                                                                                                Button background: Gray200

                                                                                                                                Button text: contentOnColorInverse(Black)

                                                                                                                                Border:1px border opaque

                                                                                                                                Dismiss button background: backgroundAlwaysLight(white) at 60% opacity

                                                                                                                                Dismiss icon color:ContentOnColorInverse(Black)

                                                                                                                                For more information, look into color customization specs.
